        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For a 24/7 on-call rotation with 1-week shifts, the minimum rotation size for sustainable coverage depends on how often you want each engineer to be on-call. Anything more frequent than every 4 weeks is considered the maximum sustainable frequency. The formula: minimum engineers = 4 (for one-in-four weeks)."
